type.description: The type of time for the autocommit period of a file in an FSx for ONTAP SnapLock volume. Setting this value to `NONE` disables autocommit. Valid values: `MINUTES`, `HOURS`, `DAYS`, `MONTHS`, `YEARS`, `NONE`.

value.description: The amount of time for the autocommit period of a file in an FSx for ONTAP SnapLock volume.
